 DNS injection
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Through the use of &lt;a href="https://ooni.io/install/"&gt;OONI Probe&lt;/a&gt;, Wikipedia domains have been &lt;a href="https://api.ooni.io/files/by_country/CN"&gt;tested&lt;/a&gt; from multiple local vantage points in China since 2015. Most measurements have been collected from China Telecom (AS4134).  &lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>